headline.main: Canada's Part in Aid to Russia

lead_paragraph: OTTAWA, Nov. 3 (Canadian Press) -- Canadian aid to Russia included war supplies, food, medical supplies and transport equipment. Prime Minister King told the House of Commons today.
abstract: Prime Min King revs Canadian developments since June, Commons
